article.description: — Martez Robinson had 20 points in Delaware State's 77-73 win against Mount St. Mary's on Saturday.
article.headline: Delaware State secures 77-73 victory against Mount St. Mary's
article.linkText: Delaware State secures 77-73 victory against Mount St. Mary's
article.story: DOVER, Del. -- — Martez Robinson had 20 points in Delaware State's 77-73 win against Mount St. Mary's on Saturday. Robinson added five rebounds for the Hornets (7-9). Jevin Muniz added 18 points, seven rebounds, five assists, and three steals. Deywilk Tavarez finished with 12 points and eight rebounds. The Mountaineers (5-8) were led in scoring by Dakota Leffew, who finished with 21 points and six rebounds. Dallas Hobbs added 16 points, six rebounds, five assists and three steals and Deshayne Montgomery had 13 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
